```bash
# Backend
docker compose -f docker-compose.qa.yml --env-file .env.qa up -d --force-recreate api-qa

# Solver
cd solver_v2
docker compose -f docker-compose.qa.yml up -d --force-recreate solver-api
```

Wait ~10s for health checks to pass.

