## 5. Docker-compose changes summary

**`mock_data_v2/database_application_v2/docker/Dockerfile.postgres`**:
Added two new COPY lines for the Fix #16 migrations. Numbering
shifted: `init-db.sh` moved from 13 → 15 to keep it last in
alphabetical init-order.

```diff
  COPY ../database/schema_planner_assignments.sql /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/12-schema-planner-assignments.sql
+ COPY ../database/schema_solver_jobs_add_fetch_flags.sql /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/13-schema-solver-jobs-add-fetch-flags.sql
+ COPY ../database/schema_planner_assignments_add_category_priority.sql /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/14-schema-planner-assignments-add-category-priority.sql
- COPY ../database/init-db.sh /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/13-init-db.sh
+ COPY ../database/init-db.sh /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/15-init-db.sh

...

- RUN chmod +x /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/13-init-db.sh
+ RUN chmod +x /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/15-init-db.sh
```

**No changes to any `docker-compose*.yml`** — the migrations are baked
into the postgres image via the Dockerfile.

**No changes to solver's Dockerfile or docker-compose** — code-only.

